code: @Override public String resolveThemeName(HttpServletRequest request) {     String themeName = (String) WebUtils.getSessionAttribute(request, THEME_SESSION_ATTRIBUTE_NAME).     // A specific theme indicated, or do we need to fallback to the default?     return (themeName != null ? themeName : getDefaultThemeName()). }

@Override public void setThemeName(HttpServletRequest request, @Nullable HttpServletResponse response, @Nullable String themeName) {     WebUtils.setSessionAttribute(request, THEME_SESSION_ATTRIBUTE_NAME, (StringUtils.hasText(themeName) ? themeName : null)). }
